PrecisApproval of amendments made to the AECB COST RECOVERY FEES REGULATIONS, 1993 that mainly correct minor administrative errors, change the French term "chantier(s) d'utilisation" to "endroits(s)", introduce fees for two new licensed activities, and reinstate the category and the fee for beta backscatter gauges.
